        <updateDate>2019-04-24T20:30:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Options Markets Stability Act</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;directs the Federal Reserve Board, the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation, and the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency to revise the method of calculating the risk, for purposes of&nbsp;satisfying capital rules applicable to depository institutions and depository institution holding companies,&nbsp;of&nbsp;certain options cleared through a central counterparty. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
